      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric dimensions sourced from lot-specific measurements or certified material test reports; input distributions characterized from measured data.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and ultimate tensile strength drawn from certified material test reports for the production Ti-6Al-4V lot. Geometric dimensions measured on five representative screws and rods using CMM; tolerances incorporated into the UQ input distributions. A screening sensitivity study was performed to identify the most influential input parameters and its findings were used to prioritize the UQ sampling effort; the study confirmed that rod diameter and yield strength were the leading contributors to QoI variance. Input characterization judged complete at level 3."
