      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios or at minimum replicate ASTM F1717 standard conditions with documented environmental controls.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed strictly under ASTM F1717 standard conditions (ambient temperature, single load level, axial-bending configuration). Only one test condition evaluated; no variation in load angle, temperature, or rod-to-screw offset distance. Achieved level 2 is below the required level 3; this is the single factor shortfall acknowledged in the COU description.",
